    {
      "id": "PopularPost9728",
      "post_content": "Fun with Kokusho. Swing for five, sac for five, then they lose five = 15dmg dealt and you gain five life. Instant speed, good finisher to just hang around until you need it. Plus the wording says, *loses* 5 life, that means it cant be prevented or redirected.\n  \n   \nAlso, it makes me laugh when I play it knowing I'm losing next turn anyways. ",
